channel.title: Can't find where to put in servers IP
channel.description:
Does anyone know how i can connect my server and put it up? I really just want that =\ I want to put it up and log in and give myself the highest rights possible. I got a 614 cache, i put it in my C: and got the source and client. Wouldn't you find client.java and then put in the ip of the server like legitpkers.no-ip.biz?
So i serached in client.java and i searched server ip, serverip and server = and i cant find any of those, I just cant put this server up!
Is there some other way to connect my server or do i need to do it some other way or what? =\ I have no options because i cant put in my servers ip..
